==PWR Live== {{Infobox Wrestling event |name=PWR Live |image= |caption= |promotion=[[Philippine Wrestling Revolution]] |date={{dts|2015|08|15}}<ref name="live815pwr">{{cite web | url=http://www.pwrcentral.com/pwr-live-results-81515/| title=PWR LIVE 08.15.15| accessdate= August 24, 2016 | publisher= PWR Central}}</ref> |venue=Makati Square Arena |city=[[Makati|Makati City, Philippines]] |liveevent=y |event= PWR Live |lastevent=[[List of Philippine Wrestling Revolution events#Wrevolution X_.282015.29|Wrevolution X (2015)]] |nextevent=[[List of Philippine Wrestling Revolution events#Renaissance_.282015.29| Renaissance (2015)]] |lastevent2=''First'' |nextevent2=[[List of Philippine Wrestling Revolution events#PWR_Live_2|PWR Live 2]] }} ''PWR Live'' events take place between major PWR events. This first edition featured the start of a tournament for the inaugural Philippine Hybrid X (PHX) Championship, which will be crowned at next month's ''Renaissance''.
