==Terminus (2015)== {{Infobox Wrestling event |name=Terminus (2015) |image= |caption= |promotion=[[Philippine Wrestling Revolution]] |date={{dts|2015|12|19}}<ref name="term15pwr">{{cite web | url=http://www.pwrcentral.com/pwr-terminus-2016/| title=PWR Terminus 2015|date=December 23, 2015| accessdate= November 13, 2016 | publisher= PWR Central}}</ref> |venue=iAcademy Auditorium |city=[[Makati|Makati City, Philippines]] |liveevent=y |event=Terminus |lastevent=[[List of Philippine Wrestling Revolution events#PWR_Live_2|PWR Live 2]] |nextevent=[[List of Philippine Wrestling Revolution events#PWR_Live:_Road_to_Vendetta|PWR Live: Road to Vendetta]] |lastevent2=[[List of Philippine Wrestling Revolution events#Terminus_.282014.29|Terminus (2014)]] |nextevent2=TBD }} The Path of Gold trophy was first awarded at this event. Its holder earns the right to challenge either the PWR champion or the PHX champion at any time within the next 12 months. It would later become a regular fixture in Terminus events.
